{"tid":830634,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發]柒鼠一家親(續集 有圖)","createTime":"2018-09-21T10:08:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-09T20:22:34.000Z","uid":105480,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"baf99f3379b98792e58c9b93b3bba2ef88ac0050","tid":830634,"uid":105480,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:08:32.000Z","msg":"話說前排有隻柒鼠入我房玩保護色 以為我見佢唔到<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/175943_e837876de54ef91a7898059c5c3bcf0f.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F175943_e837876de54ef91a7898059c5c3bcf0f.png&h=8824eea8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n   我二話不說攞把滅鼠掃將佢亂棍拍死<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/180208_81f683946a1fec03cf2838322c0a0115.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F180208_81f683946a1fec03cf2838322c0a0115.png&h=6809d80b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n  直到頭先見到有隻柒鼠二號喺我房門徘徊 我即刻閂房門逼佢入廚房 過咗一陣就中撚咗㭍鼠陷阱 <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/09/21/180553_e6b5d70dbdc6c9af30b41256959d18c8.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F09%2F21%2F180553_e6b5d70dbdc6c9af30b41256959d18c8.png&h=447ca0a3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n 諗緊點樣處置佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">食鼠有鼠味</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d776558a1628e3e4121c2a26318f0f83de9a4e15","tid":830634,"uid":78349,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-21T10:09:33.000Z","msg":"好心你清潔下自己屋企 捉到咁多老鼠仲要咁撚自豪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29d9b88ae61a6ba34d2f092065cdda3b07fcaf8f","tid":830634,"uid":158469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":